Subject: [PATCH] fix incompatibility with vcrpy 2

---
 .travis.yml                                 | 13 +++++++------
 test-requirements.txt                       |  2 +-
 tests/fixtures/ssl_tunnel.yaml              |  2 +-
 tests/fixtures/ssl_tunnel_http_failure.yaml |  2 +-
